        <item>
            <title>Honda 將 Pokemon 實體化成電單車，靈感來自《Pokemon 朱》神獸 Koraidon</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/honda-pokemon-koraidon/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=honda-pokemon-koraidon</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/honda-pokemon-koraidon/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 06:14:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Honda]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokemon]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294639</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本本田技研工業（Honda）與 Pokémon 公司合作，推出以《Pokémon 朱》傳説神獸「故勒頓」（Koraidon）為藍本的實體電單車「Honda 故勒頓」。這款幾乎等比例的未來主義車種將於 2025 年 3 月 7 日至 3 月 9 日，在東京本田青山迎賓廣場展出。Honda 表示，該項目結合尖端技術，力求還原故勒頓的設計與特性。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294647" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/037screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/037screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/037screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「Honda 故勒頓」在尺寸與重量上貼近遊戲中的設定，並融入本田獨有的自平衡技術。此技術源於 2017 年 CES 展公開的「Honda Riding Assist」，借鑒 ASIMO 機器人的平衡控制原理。據本田透露，未來版本有望實現故勒頓的「疾馳形態」及四足行走功能，展現動態魅力。展覽期間雖未提供試駕，但其細膩設計已令人期待。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294645" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hondakoraidonpokemon-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hondakoraidonpokemon-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hondakoraidonpokemon.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>據日媒報導，Toyota 於 2024 年曾推出《Pokemon 紫》的神獸「密勒頓」（Miraidon）實體電單車，開啟車廠與 Pokémon 合作的先河。Honda 今次以「Koraidon」為題，似有與對手一較高下之意。業界人士分析，Honda 憑藉機車製造經驗，或能在技術層面超越 Toyota 的展示型設計，進一步提升實用性與觀賞性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294646" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/036screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/036screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/036screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「Honda 故勒頓」展示技術實力之餘，也標誌著動漫文化與汽車工業的深度融合。展覽過後，業界預料 Honda 或會進一步完善此概念車，甚至探索量產可能。隨著 Pokémon 熱潮持續，未來或有更多車廠加入這場創意競賽，為市場帶來新驚喜。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_12249"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ryoEWpD9NMg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.cool-style.com.tw/wd2/archives/1167841-%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%84%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80%EF%BC%81honda-%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%AF%B6%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%A2-%E6%9C%B1%E3%80%8B%E7%A5%9E%E7%8D%B8%E3%80%8C%E6%95%85%E5%8B%92%E9%A0%93%E3%80%8D">COOL</a>、<a href="https://www.siliconera.com/honda-teases-pokemon-koraidon-appearance-in-real-life/">siliconear</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
