        </item>
        <item>
            <title>小米 15 Ultra 發表: 首部支持奧斯卡 ACES 電影色彩系統 Android 手機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/xiaomi-15-ultra/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xiaomi-15-ultra</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/xiaomi-15-ultra/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[天恩]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:35:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294557</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米於 2025 年 2 月 27 日晚正式發布旗艦機型 Xiaomi 15 Ultra，搭載 Snapdragon 8 Elite 處理器，售價由 6,499 人民幣起。新機主打 Leica 四攝系統，其中 200MP 遠攝鏡頭備受矚目，並推出拼色設計向 Leica 致敬。國際版將於 3 月在巴塞隆納 MWC 大會亮相，香港上市詳情待公佈。</p><h2></h2><h2>外觀與設計</h2><p>Xiaomi 15 Ultra 延續圓形相機模組設計，推出黑、白、黑銀及綠銀四款配色，其中拼色版本靈感源自 Leica 相機，背面採用荔枝皮紋理。機身重 226g，厚 9.35mm，具 IP68 防塵防水功能，並支援雙喇叭及四咪高風配置。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gkzaxxfwmaas3q.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294564" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gkzaxxfwmaas3q-694x489.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="489" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gkzaxxfwmaas3q-694x489.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gkzaxxfwmaas3q.jpeg 1278w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/508744c64a3f6385ebe2.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/508744c64a3f6385ebe2-694x496.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="496" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/508744c64a3f6385ebe2-694x496.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/508744c64a3f6385ebe2.jpeg 1002w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c734d307f4d1c3aadc6b.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c734d307f4d1c3aadc6b-694x578.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="578" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c734d307f4d1c3aadc6b-694x578.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c734d307f4d1c3aadc6b.jpeg 1013w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>專業影像體驗</h2><p>新機配備 Leica 四攝系統（14-100mm），包括 1 吋  50MP Sony LYT-900 主攝及 200MP Samsung HP9 遠攝鏡頭，4 鏡，光學焦距等效 14mm / 23mm / 70mm / 100mm。支援 28 倍無損變焦及 8K 錄影，另有專屬影像套裝，包括濾鏡轉接環及具 2,000mAh 電池的握把，提升拍攝靈活性。在拍片方面，小米是 Android 首部支持奧斯卡 ACES 電影色彩系統</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/37fefbb0f4ff11efbfa5.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/37fefbb0f4ff11efbfa5-694x365.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/37fefbb0f4ff11efbfa5-694x365.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/37fefbb0f4ff11efbfa5.jpeg 959w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>規格與性能</h2><p>配備 6.73 吋 2K+ AMOLED 螢幕，亮度達 3,200 尼特，支援 120Hz LTPO。電池容量 6,000mAh，提供 90W 有線及 80W 無線充電。處理器為 Snapdragon 8 Elite，搭配 LPDDR5X RAM 與 UFS 4.1 儲存。隨 MWC 臨近，更多細節或將公佈，值得關注其本地定價與發售安排。</p><h2>官方樣本</h2><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/21b70f425c6acdaa7cb1.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294565" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/21b70f425c6acdaa7cb1-399x580.jpeg" alt="" width="399" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/21b70f425c6acdaa7cb1-399x580.jpeg 399w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/21b70f425c6acdaa7cb1.jpeg 618w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 399px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/688bdde736457a742fae.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294566" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/688bdde736457a742fae-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/688bdde736457a742fae-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/688bdde736457a742fae.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cbd5735690f621b77fc3.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cbd5735690f621b77fc3-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cbd5735690f621b77fc3-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cbd5735690f621b77fc3.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ea4acb4c4fc4009ce901.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ea4acb4c4fc4009ce901-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ea4acb4c4fc4009ce901-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ea4acb4c4fc4009ce901.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/83bba56b3e1bba8d3a6e.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/83bba56b3e1bba8d3a6e-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/83bba56b3e1bba8d3a6e-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/83bba56b3e1bba8d3a6e.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294570" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4-686x580.jpeg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/xiaomi-15-ultra/mobile-phone/">小米 15 Ultra 發表: 首部支持奧斯卡 ACES 電影色彩系統 Android 手機</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
